6891          ManualBranchSegmentMWFlow(LossBranch(ACbranch(t,br)),los,fd) $ { ( ord(los) <= branchLossBlocks(ACbranch) ) and validLossSegment(ACbranch,los,fd) and ( ACBRANCHFLOWDIRECTED.l(ACbranch,fd) > 0 ) }
